About
You're looking for the kind of performance that feels more serendipitous than scripted: where there's a special kind of magic that passes between performers and the audience - where the set list is never the same and you can always count on an encore. At Dolby Live, you're never far from the magic in one of the theater's 5,200 seats. The breathtaking Dolby Atmos sound system is custom-designed and built into the venueâ€™s thoughtful design, delivering a transformative music experience you can't get anywhere else. Every event that is performed and mixed in Dolby Atmos, from concerts and sports to awards shows and conventions, feels more intimate and immersive. Come for the show. Stay for the live experience.
